{"tid":1849661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"難怪支那感染人數咁少","createTime":"2020-01-29T07:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T08:38:04.000Z","uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfc2d28f2181e0ff7e5023513614a708b8e5fa1","tid":1849661,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"原来发烧咳嗽去医院要求查是否武汉肺炎的检测需要付2000元才给做&hellip;&hellip;所以，官方的确诊数字&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4a7a19ff7eef40d28a8143371ca6abdd5d4bf6","tid":1849661,"uid":249317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"Ching會唔會太遲？"},{"pid":"7d52601ce324734ebcb1f1c1fde58fcd569e4094","tid":1849661,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d904922806521f0684bc4ca9e52138b5ddaa36eb","tid":1849661,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=b71e8d82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=8d862730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=7561968f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=28fa506c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=37cdc8e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=b5106e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=f0889489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fnpptl%2Ftopics%2Frespirators%2Ffactsheets%2Frespsars.html&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=e9984421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html</a><br />\nSARS 時期CDC 對N95 同防毒面具嘅指引<br />\n（僅供參考！WARS 嘅傳染性係SARS 嘅一倍以上！！！！）"},{"pid":"5334d4543ba5b00858e73ea1770c2a675eca0f3c","tid":1849661,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"今日佳句，鸡国终于有了可以媲美前苏联笑话的作品了&darr;<br />\n问：&ldquo;如果有人穿越回一个月前的武汉，他能拯救这场灾难吗？&rdquo;&nbsp;<br />\n答：&ldquo;不，他会成为第九个造谣的人。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a59b8f96745c94d24a543182e302cfd2a14c6857","tid":1849661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c55a467665fe35dfd9dbc3ff316bb2dda620e7","tid":1849661,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5334d4543ba5b00858e73ea1770c2a675eca0f3c","tid":1849661,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"今日佳句，鸡国终于有了可以媲美前苏联笑话的作品了&darr;<br />\n问：&ldquo;如果有人穿越回一个月前的武汉，他能拯救这场灾难吗？&rdquo;&nbsp;<br />\n答：&ldquo;不，他会成为第九个造谣的人。&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f78e7275fb1c6a2ed99c239da26a4d66685769","tid":1849661,"uid":279779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5334d4543ba5b00858e73ea1770c2a675eca0f3c","tid":1849661,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"今日佳句，鸡国终于有了可以媲美前苏联笑话的作品了&darr;<br />\n问：&ldquo;如果有人穿越回一个月前的武汉，他能拯救这场灾难吗？&rdquo;&nbsp;<br />\n答：&ldquo;不，他会成为第九个造谣的人。&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}